data.description: Just Reduced. Extraordinary SantaFe style home. You're welcomed into the courtyard & through the rustic yet stylish front door. An open floor plan guides you into the enormous living room where you'll admire the customized viga beams running across an elevated ceiling and a divine kiva inspired fireplace. The zoned primary suite allows for tranquil living while the second primary extends a space for guests to feel at home in. Rich natural wood trims and finishes throughout, give elegant yet earthy vibes. If storage is a necessity, this home offers a large pantry, two linen closets, multiple walk-in closets, several storage spaces in the garage plus a Tuff shed out back. Dual Nest thermostats keep a comfortable temperature. All this and much more awaits so call now to make this Pueblo revival your new sanctuary today.
